{"text_id":134018,"tokens":["We"," present"," a"," dynamic"," prediction"," framework"," for"," binary"," sequences"," that"," is"," based"," on"," a"," Bernoulli"," generalization"," of"," the"," auto","-","reg","ressive"," process","."," Our"," approach"," lends"," itself"," easily"," to"," variants"," of"," the"," standard"," AR"," (","1",")"," model",","," where"," the"," predictions"," are"," based"," on"," the"," current"," or"," lagged"," values"," of"," the"," series","."," The"," model"," is"," flexible"," in"," that"," it"," can"," allow"," an"," arbitrary"," (","finite",")"," number"," of"," past"," observations"," to"," affect"," the"," prediction","."," We"," show"," that"," the"," new"," model"," and"," the"," standard"," AR"," (","1",")"," model"," are"," both"," special"," cases"," of"," a"," general"," model"," for"," dynamic"," prediction"," and"," provide"," necessary"," and"," sufficient"," conditions"," for"," a"," given"," model"," to"," be"," the"," general"," model","."," We"," also"," discuss"," how"," the"," proposed"," framework"," can"," be"," used"," to"," make"," predictions"," for"," non","-","binary"," sequences","."," We"," use"," simulated"," data"," and"," real","-","life"," data"," to"," demonstrate"," the"," performance"," of"," the"," model","."],"sub_source":"sci_gen","model":"13B","label":1}